  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're stranded on a sinking ship with a limited set of items. Combine them creatively to unlock new locations, uncover hidden secrets, and discover multiple endings - each choice brings a wild outcome!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pop-Culture References</strong>: A world filled with quirky, nostalgic nods (mostly from <i>SpongeBob) </i> to keep you looking for easter eggs along the way.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/c0fc9c98ad219107b6ffa15277efe5a2.poster.avif?t=1768714412\" width=424 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/c0fc9c98ad219107b6ffa15277efe5a2.webm?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/c0fc9c98ad219107b6ffa15277efe5a2.mp4?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bugs Collecting</strong>: Hunt down rare and ridiculous bugs scattered throughout the world. Some are dangerous. Some are just weird. All of them are worth finding.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/05022e339f7a117b55f7e188cd178cbc.poster.avif?t=1768714412\" width=424 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/05022e339f7a117b55f7e188cd178cbc.webm?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/05022e339f7a117b55f7e188cd178cbc.mp4?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death is Just Part of the Journey</strong>: Made the wrong move? Congrats, you found another ridiculous way to die.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/47ee59d18e6deee7e5b789d93a8b11bc.poster.avif?t=1768714412\" width=424 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/47ee59d18e6deee7e5b789d93a8b11bc.webm?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/47ee59d18e6deee7e5b789d93a8b11bc.mp4?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Absurd Humor and Puzzles</strong>: Enjoy bizarre challenges, unpredictable twists, and lmao moments as you make your way through the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/bf0b3c3f87a8bf803631c3b6280fd53b.poster.avif?t=1768714412\" width=424 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/bf0b3c3f87a8bf803631c3b6280fd53b.webm?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347290/extras/bf0b3c3f87a8bf803631c3b6280fd53b.mp4?t=1768714412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
